longBusinessSummary: Suprajit Engineering Limited manufactures and sells automotive cables, halogen lamps, speedometers, and other automotive components in India, the United States, the United Kingdom, Germany, and Luxembourg. The company provides control cables, halogen and LED bulbs, electro-mechanical actuators, digital clusters, and friction products, as well as combined braking, complete braking, and throttle position systems. It also provides gear box, braking system, throttle controls, linear actuation, display cluster and telematics, gear shifter systems, lighting systems, and USB charging modules. Suprajit Engineering Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
